article_title: Sen. Jon Erpenbach: Bill gives Wisconsin another chance at health care funds
article_text:
Madison, WI (53711)

Today

Thunderstorms this morning, then partly cloudy during the afternoon hours. High near 85F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms overnight. Low 64F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 50%.

og.description: The SAME Act, sponsored by Sen. Tammy Baldwin and others, would let states get 100 percent funding for Medicaid expansion for four years even if they didn't take the funding
